  "remarks": "Voentekstilprom manufactures clothing for the needs of the Government of the Russian Federation. It has provided clothing supplies to the Russian military as part of a State defence order. It manufactures field uniforms for the National Guard of Russia and shirts for soldiers of the Russian Navy and the National Guard of Russia.",
